arriscando nossas vidas.

263
00:17:27,212 --> 00:17:28,672
Já chega.

264
00:17:28,756 --> 00:17:29,965
Libere o plasma,

265
00:17:30,049 --> 00:17:32,509
ou quando voltarmos à nave, e voltaremos,

266
00:17:32,593 --> 00:17:34,595
eu o prendo e aí você pensa em culpa

267
00:17:34,678 --> 00:17:37,264
enquanto espera a corte marcial
por desobedecer a ordens.

268
00:17:37,347 --> 00:17:39,141
Entendeu, Especialista Tyler?

269
00:17:39,224 --> 00:17:41,560
Iniciando liberação de plasma, senhor.

270
00:17:49,318 --> 00:17:52,029
