299
00:19:12,901 --> 00:19:14,903
Porque o Spock tinha dificuldades.

300
00:19:15,654 --> 00:19:17,156
Dificuldades humanas.

301
00:19:18,699 --> 00:19:19,533
Para aprender.

302
00:19:20,784 --> 00:19:21,618
Para ler.

303
00:19:22,286 --> 00:19:23,120
Para escrever.

304
00:19:24,079 --> 00:19:29,042
